reviewText:
To note: If you are purchasing these DVDs for the French language option, only one of the two DVDs has a French language track (Dora's Fantastic Gymnastics Adventure). The other DVD, Dora's Ballet Adventures, is in English only.

Veuillez noter que dans cette emballage de deux DVDs, seulement un DVD, Dora fait de la gymnastique, offre une piste sonore en franais. L'autre, Dora's Ballet Adventures, est en anglais uniquement.
Bought for granddaughter BIRTHDAY a fun gift and entertain ed
3 year old and 18mo. Old loved it.  I expect to have it memorized soon.
